gallery-dl
----------
Version: 1.31.7
Source:  https://github.com/mikf/gallery-dl
License: GPL-2.0-only

gallery-dl is free software licensed under the GNU General Public License
version 2. Source code is available at https://github.com/mikf/gallery-dl.

On macOS, gallery-dl is distributed as a Python wheel and invoked via a
wrapper script that calls `python3 -m gallery_dl`. On Windows and Linux,
the standalone executable from the official releases is used.

gallery-dl is invoked as a subprocess.


